issue.description:
By adding th number of version to each js call, we'll force the loading of new javascript files in client cache.

exemple in the resource view : 
<pre>
$xml = JFactory::getXML(JPATH_ADMINISTRATOR .'/components/com_easysdi_core/easysdi_core.xml');
$version = (string)$xml->version;

$document = JFactory::getDocument();
$document->addScript('administrator/components/com_easysdi_core/libraries/easysdi/view/view.js?v='.$version);
</pre>
